Text: Tackar Tackar, mer sånt här om någon har?

oswald63, you may not realize this but Canada is a bilingual country.  We have two official languages, English and French.  CBC produces programs in both languages, so the fact that "CBC= Canadian Broadcast Corporation" is not helpful.

Though, I would assume that because the title "Conspiracy theory - CBC - The Fifth Estate" is in English, that this release will also be in English.
